name: Five fairies paperdoll download
description:
These five paper doll fairies are printed from your computer so that you can cut them out and assemble them.

These are the easiest paper dolls to put together that I have designed so far.

Here is what you get;

Links to two PDF files to download high resolution illustrations to print out and assemble.

3 pages of instructions, how to photos and finished models and ideas and tips.

5 pages of paper dolls in full color to print out, put together and embellish. There is a total of 8 pages.

There is a list of supplies:
White card-stock, glue, scissors, ribbon, hole punch, plus a few extras to make your dolls sturdy.

These make great gifts, for swaps, presents, gift enclosures and even ornaments. they can be embellished with stickers, scrapbook paper, ephemera, or chipboard and rubber stamps, but look great as they are. You can make them many times in different ways.

The dolls are made to be printed on 8.5 x 11 letter size paper, but if you have the software you may enlarge them or reduce them to fit your needs. the finished height of the dolls is approx 7-10 inches (they vary in size)

The files will be delivered as a link in your e-mail, that downloads in one click. The files are available for 3 days before they expire.

If you need more time just e-mail me and I will send them again.

Please let me know the e-mail address that you want the files sent to. Also be sure to check your spam folder in case your e-mail provider directs them there.
